<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>国际邮轮度假中心 登录页</title>
    <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/cruiseLiner.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<div class="title01">
    <i class="loginico01"></i><span>用户登录&绑定微信号</span>
</div>
<div class="cont01">
    <div class="box01">
        <p>登陆&绑定微信号后，你可以直接将产品信息转发，转发内容将以您设定的公司名称及个人信息向客户展现！</p>
        <p>客户不流失，销售尽掌握！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="loginbox">
        <form class="form-horizontal" action="/dologin" method="post" role="form">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="loginName" class="col-xs-4 control-label loginlable">用户名</label>
                <div class="col-xs-6">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control input-sm" id="loginName" name="loginName" placeholder="邮箱/手机号码">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password" class="col-xs-4 control-label loginlable">密码</label>
                <div class="col-xs-6">
                    <input type="password" class="form-control input-sm" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-6">
                    <input type="hidden" id="openid" name="openid" value="<%=openid%>">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-xs loginBtn">登  录</button>
                    <!--<a href="#" class="loginForgetPw" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#findPW">忘记密码</a>-->
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="box01">
        <p>如您没有注册过荟邮轮，<br>请登录<a href="#">www.huiyoulun.com</a>进行注册。</p>
        <div class="loginNotice">如您有任何疑问，请拨打<span>400-998-6121</span></div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="loginadv"></div>
<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="findPW" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog login-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header modal-headerbor">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <!--<h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">找回密码</h4>-->
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form class="form-horizontal" role="form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-xs-4 control-label loginlable">注册邮箱</label>
                        <div class="col-xs-6">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control input-sm" id="" placeholder="输入您的注册邮箱">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-6">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-xs loginBtn">确  定</button>
                            <a href="#" class="findPWcancel" data-dismiss="modal">取消</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
